task.action:
Edit `src/app/globals.css`. Add the following utility classes:
      1. Scrollbar hide:
         ```css
         .scrollbar-hide {
           scrollbar-width: none;
         }
         .scrollbar-hide::-webkit-scrollbar {
           display: none;
         }
         ```
      2. Group expand/collapse via grid-template-rows:
         ```css
         .nav-group-content {
           display: grid;
           grid-template-rows: 0fr;
           transition: grid-template-rows 200ms ease-out;
         }
         .nav-group-content[data-expanded="true"] {
           grid-template-rows: 1fr;
         }
         .nav-group-content > div {
           overflow: hidden;
         }
         ```
      3. Reduced motion override:
         ```css
         @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
           .nav-group-content {
             transition: none;
           }
         }
         ```
